name: GEO_BENE_SK
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ASSIGNED SURROGATE KEY USED TO IDENTIFY A BENEFICIARYS ZIP CODE, AND ESTABLISHES UNIQUENESS OF A CLAIM. THIS IS A COMPONENT OF THE CLAIM 4 AND 5-PART KEYS USED FOR JOINING CLAIMS.

name: CLM_DT_SGNTR_SK
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ASSIGNED SURROGATE KEY IDENTIFYING A DISTINCT COMBINATION OF RELATED DATES USED TO ESTABLISH UNIQUENESS OF A CLAIM. THE DISTINCT COMBINATION OF DATE GROUPINGS IS A COMPONENT OF THE CLAIM 4 AND 5-PART KEYS.

name: CLM_TYPE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE SOURCE AND TYPE OF CLAIM SUBMITTED THROUGH THE MEDICARE OR MEDICAID PROGRAM.  FOR EXAMPLE:  60 = MEDICARE  NATIONAL CLAIMS HISTORY (NCH) INPATIENT CLAIM   8900 = MEDICAID FEE FOR SERVICE DENTAL     REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_TYPE_CD

name: CLM_NUM_SK
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ASSIGNED SURROGATE KEY USED TO DIFFERENTIATE CLAIMS THAT HAVE COMMON GEOGRAPHY, CLAIM DATES AND CLAIM TYPES. WHEN THE SAME COMBINATION OF GEO_BENE_SK, CLM_DT_SGNTR_SK, AND CLM_TYPE_CD IS NOT UNIQUE, THE CLM_NUM_SK IS SEQUENCED TO MAKE THE 4 AND 5 PART KEYS UNIQUE.  THIS IS A COMPONENT OF THE CLAIM 4 AND 5-PART KEYS USED FOR JOINING CLAIMS.

name: GEO_BENE_EFCTV_SK
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ASSIGNED SURROGATE EFFECTIVE KEY USED TO IDENTIFY A BENEFICIARYS ZIP CODE, AND ESTABLISHES UNIQUENESS OF A CLAIM. THIS IS A COMPONENT OF THE CLAIM 4 AND 5-PART KEYS USED FOR JOINING CLAIMS AND GROUPING CLAIM FAMILIES.

name: CLM_DT_SGNTR_EFCTV_SK
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ASSIGNED SURROGATE EFFECTIVE KEY IDENTIFYING A DISTINCT COMBINATION OF RELATED DATES USED TO ESTABLISH UNIQUENESS OF A CLAIM. THE DISTINCT COMBINATION OF DATE GROUPINGS IS A COMPONENT OF THE CLAIM 4 AND 5-PART EFFECTIVE KEYS USED FOR JOINING CLAIMS AND GROUPING CLAIM FAMILIES.

name: CLM_TYPE_EFCTV_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE SOURCE AND TYPE OF CLAIM SUBMITTED THROUGH THE MEDICARE OR MEDICAID PROGRAM.  FOR EXAMPLE:  60 = MEDICARE  NATIONAL CLAIMS HISTORY (NCH) INPATIENT CLAIM   8900 = MEDICAID FEE FOR SERVICE DENTAL     REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_TYPE_CD

name: CLM_NUM_EFCTV_SK
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ASSIGNED SURROGATE EFFECTIVE KEY USED TO DIFFERENTIATE CLAIMS THAT HAVE COMMON GEOGRAPHY, CLAIM DATES AND CLAIM TYPES. WHEN THE SAME COMBINATION OF GEO_BENE_SK, CLM_DT_SGNTR_SK, AND CLM_TYPE_CD IS NOT UNIQUE, THE CLM_NUM_EFCTV_SK IS SEQUENCED TO MAKE THE 4 AND 5 PART KEYS UNIQUE. THIS IS A COMPONENT OF THE CLAIM 4 AND 5-PART EFFECTIVE KEYS USED FOR JOINING CLAIMS AND GROUPING CLAIM FAMILIES.

name: CLM_EFCTV_DT
comment: A DATE CORRESPONDING TO THE NATIONAL CLAIM HISTORY (NCH) WEEKLY PROCESSING DATE AND USED IN FINAL ACTION PROCESSING TO IDENTIFY A VERSION OF A CLAIM. IT WILL ALWAYS BE A FRIDAY DATE.

name: CLM_OBSLT_DT
comment: A DATE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) INDICATING IF A CLAIM IS FINAL ACTION OR THE LATEST VERSION. WHEN A CLAIM IS FINAL ACTION/LATEST VERSION, DATE 12/31/9999 WILL BE PRESENT. OTHERWISE, THE DATE WILL BE SET TO THE NATIONAL CLAIM HISTORY (NCH) WEEKLY CLAIM PROCESSING DATE OF THE PRIOR VERSION OF THE CLAIM. IT WILL ALWAYS BE A FRIDAY DATE.

name: BENE_CTGRY_EQTBL_BIC_CD
comment: A CODE THAT GROUPS BENEFICIARY IDENTIFICATION CODES (BICS) UNDER ONE CATEGORY THAT SHARE SIMILAR RELATIONSHIPS  BETWEEN A BENEFICIARY AND THE PRIMARY WAGE EARNER. THE EQUATABLE BIC MODULE ELECTRONICALLY MATCHES TWO RECORDS THAT CONTAIN DIFFERENT BICS WHERE IT IS APPARENT THAT BOTH ARE RECORDS FOR THE SAME BENEFICIARY.  IT VALIDATES THE BIC AND RETURNS A BASE BIC UNDER WHICH TO HOUSE THE RECORD IN THE NATIONAL CLAIMS HISTORY (NCH) DATABASES. (ALL RECORDS FOR A BENEFICIARY ARE STORED UNDER A SINGLE BIC.)

name: BENE_SK
comment: A UNIQUE NUMBER ASSIGNED BY THE ENROLLMENT DATA BASE (EDB) TO EACH EDB RECORD TO IDENTIFY A BENEFICIARY.

name: BENE_LINK_KEY
comment: AN UNIQUE NUMBER ASSIGNED BY THE ENROLLMENT DATABASE (EDB) TO EACH EDB BENEFICIARY RECORD.     NOTE: THIS COLUMN IS ONLY POPULATED WHEN THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) RECEIVES A BENE_LINK_KEY FROM THE SOURCE SYSTEM.

name: CLM_ADJSTMT_TYPE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE TYPE OF ADJUSTMENT RECORD REPRESENTED ON A CLAIM OR ENCOUNTER.    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_ADJSTMT_TYPE_CD

name: CLM_ADJSTMT_RSN_CD
comment: A FISCAL INTERMEDIARY SHARED SYSTEM (FISS) INTERNAL CODE IDENTIFYING THE TYPE OF ADJUSTMENT BEING PERFORMED.   FOR EXAMPLE:  AA = AUTOMATED ADJUSTMENT  CR = CLAIM RECONSIDERATION    NOTE: THESE CODES ARE ASSIGNED AND MAINTAINED BY EACH MEDICARE ADMINISTRATIVE CONTRACTOR (MAC) EXCEPT FOR THOSE THAT ARE HARD-CODED BY FISS.

name: CLM_ALOWD_CHRG_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING THE SUM OF ALL THE LINE ITEM ALLOWED CHARGES ON A CLAIM.

name: CLM_ALOWD_CHRG_CD
comment: NOT DEFINED, BECAUSE THIS COLUMN IS CURRENTLY NOT POPULATED IN THE IDR AND THE DATA IS NOT PROVIDED BY THE SOURCE.

name: CLM_BENE_COPMT_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING A FLAT FEE COPAYMENT PAID BY A BENEFICIARY AT THE TIME SERVICES WERE RENDERED.

name: CLM_BENE_PMT_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT PAID BY A BENEFICIARY FOR SERVICES RENDERED ON A CLAIM.

name: CLM_BENE_PMT_COINSRNC_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING THE PORTION OF COST THAT IS THE RESPONSIBILITY OF A BENEFICIARY FOR PAYMENT.

name: CLM_BENE_PMT_DDCTBL_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT APPLIED TO A BENEFICIARYS DEDUCTIBLE.

name: CLM_COB_PTNT_RESP_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING A BENEFICIARYS PATIENT RESPONSIBILITY ON A COORDINATION OF BENEFITS (COB) CLAIM.

name: CLM_CARDHLDR_ID
comment: AN IDENTIFIER OF A PLAN ENROLLEE FOUND ON A CLAIM.

name: CLM_CNTL_NUM
comment: AN IDENTIFIER ASSIGNED BY THE CLAIM PROCESSOR (I.E., MEDICARE ADMINISTRATIVE CONTRACTOR, PART D PLAN, OR ENCOUNTER DATA PROCESSING CONTRACTOR) TO A CLAIM.

name: CLM_CTGRY_SRVC_CD
comment: NOT DEFINED, BECAUSE THIS COLUMN IS CURRENTLY NOT POPULATED IN THE IDR AND THE DATA IS NOT PROVIDED BY THE SOURCE.

name: CLM_DISP_CD
comment: A CODE INDICATING THE DISPOSITION OR OUTCOME OF A PROCESSED CLAIM RECORD.    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_DISP_CD

name: CLM_DRVD_HDR_IND
comment: AN INDICATOR IDENTIFYING WHETHER A FUNCTION PERFORMED AT THE LINE LEVEL IS STORED AT THE HEADER.  VALID VALUES:  Y = LINE ELEMENT FUNCTION STORED AT THE HEADER.  N = DEFAULT

name: CLM_EDIT_GRP_SGNTR_SK
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ASSIGNED SURROGATE KEY THAT UNIQUELY IDENTIFIES A COMBINATION OF NATIONAL CLAIM HISTORY (NCH) EDITS WITHIN SOME SET OF CLAIMS.

name: CLM_ENCTR_PMT_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT REPORTED BY A MANAGED CARE PLAN IDENTIFYING THE EQUIVALENT THAT A FEE-FOR-SERVICE (FFS) WOULD HAVE PAID FOR A CLAIM.

name: CLM_ERR_SGNTR_SK
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ASSIGNED SURROGATE KEY THAT UNIQUELY IDENTIFIES A COMBINATION OF ERRORS THAT HAVE CO-OCCURRED WITHIN SOME SET OF CLAIMS.

name: CLM_FFS_IND
comment: A VALUE INDICATING IF A CLAIM IS FEE-FOR-SERVICE (FFS).  VALID VALUES:  Y = YES, FFS CLAIM  N = NOT FFS CLAIM

name: CLM_FINL_ACTN_IND
comment: A VALUE INDICATING A FINAL ACTION CLAIM.  VALID VALUES:   Y = FINAL ACTION CLAIM, NOT VOIDED.  N = NOT FINAL ACTION CLAIM

name: CLM_FORM_CD
comment: NOT DEFINED, BECAUSE THIS COLUMN IS CURRENTLY NOT POPULATED IN THE IDR AND THE DATA IS NOT PROVIDED BY THE SOURCE.

name: CLM_HIC_NUM
comment: A MEDICARE HEALTH INSURANCE CLAIM NUMBER (HICN) CONSISTING OF A NINE DIGIT CLAIM ACCOUNT NUMBER (CAN) FOLLOWED BY A ONE OR TWO POSITION ALPHA-NUMERIC BENEFICIARY IDENTIFICATION CODE (BIC).  THIS COLUMN CONTAINS EITHER THE SOCIAL SECURITY ADMINISTRATION (SSA) HICN OR THE RAILROAD RETIREMENT BOARD (RRB) INTERNAL HICN.

name: CLM_INVC_RCVD_DAY_CNT
comment: THE NUMBER OF DAYS TO INVOICE RECEIVED.

name: CLM_LCL_CTGRY_SRVC_CD
comment: THE SOURCE-SPECIFIC CODE DEFINING THE CATEGORY OF SERVICE UNDER WHICH THE CLAIM WAS FILED.  THESE ARE BROAD CATEGORIES AND DO NOT DESCRIBE SPECIFIC MEDICAL TREATMENTS OR PROCEDURES

name: CLM_LCL_PLAN_CD
comment: NOT DEFINED, BECAUSE THIS COLUMN IS CURRENTLY NOT POPULATED IN THE IDR AND THE DATA IS NOT PROVIDED BY THE SOURCE.

name: CLM_LCL_TYPE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING A SPECIFIC TYPE OF CLAIM SUBMITTED THROUGH THE MEDICARE OR MEDICAID PROGRAM FOR ENCOUNTERS.    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_LCL_TYPE_CD

name: CLM_LTST_CLM_IND
comment: AN INDICATOR IDENTIFYING WHETHER A CLAIM IS THE LATEST ACTION.  VALID VALUES:  Y = LATEST ACTION ON A CLAIM.  N = NOT THE LATEST ACTION ON A CLAIM. SUBSEQUENT ADJUSTMENTS OR RESUBMISSIONS TO THE CLAIM EXIST.

name: CLM_MDCD_RCPNT_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING A RECIPIENT IDENTIFIER FOR A MEDICAID BENEFICIARY.

name: CLM_MDCR_COINSRNC_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING THE PORTION APPLIED TOWARD THE COINSURANCE A BENEFICIARY IS RESPONSIBLE FOR.

name: CLM_MDCR_DDCTBL_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING THE PORTION APPLIED TOWARD THE DEDUCTIBLE A BENEFICIARY IS RESPONSIBLE FOR.

name: CLM_MDCR_XOVR_PMT_AMT
comment: THE AMOUNT PAID TO MEDICAID BY MEDICARE FOR THE CROSSOVER CLAIM.  THIS FIELD IS ZERO ON NON-MEDICARE CLAIMS. [HRMZ]

name: CLM_NCVRD_CHRG_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING THE PORTION OF A CHARGE NOT COVERED BY MEDICARE.

name: CLM_NET_CHRG_AMT
comment: TOTAL CLAIM CHARGE MINUS THIRD PARTY PAYMENT AMOUNT AND RECIPIENT PAID AMOUNT.

name: CLM_OCRNC_SGNTR_SK
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) SURROGATE KEY THAT UNIQUELY IDENTIFIES A COMBINATION OF OCCURRENCES WITHIN SOME SET OF CLAIMS.

name: CLM_ORIG_CNTL_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE ORIGINAL CLAIM CONTROL NUMBER (CCN) ON AN ADJUSTED CLAIM.

name: CLM_OTHR_TP_PD_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING HOW MUCH WAS PAID BY A THIRD PARTY PAYER.

name: CLM_PD_STUS_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE STATUS OF A CLAIM.    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_PD_STUS_CD

name: CLM_PLAN_CD
comment: CODE FOR THE PLAN OR PRODUCT LINE OF THE MEDICAL PLAN PACKAGE.

name: CLM_PMT_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING HOW MUCH WAS PAID ON AN ADJUDICATED CLAIM.

name: CLM_PMT_DAY_CNT
comment: THE NUMBER OF DAYS TO PAYMENT.

name: CLM_PRVDR_PMT_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING THE TOTAL PAYMENT MADE TO A PROVIDER/SUPPLIER FOR SERVICES RENDERED ON AN INDIVIDUAL CLAIM.

name: CLM_PTCH_GRP_SGNTR_SK
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ASSIGNED SURROGATE KEY THAT UNIQUELY IDENTIFIES A PATCH THAT WAS APPLIED TO A NATIONAL CLAIM HISTORY (NCH) CLAIM RECORD. IT IS DERIVED FROM THE NCH PATCH CODE AND CLAIM HISTORY PATCH APPLY DATE.

name: CLM_PTNT_LBLTY_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING HOW MUCH OUT OF POCKET COSTS A BENEFICIARY IS RESPONSIBLE FOR.

name: CLM_QUERY_CD
comment: INDICATION OF  THE TYPE OF CLAIM RECORD BEING PROCESSED WITH RESPECT TO PAYMENT (DEBIT/CREDIT INDICATOR - ORIGINAL, FULL, REPLACEMENT; INTERIM/FINAL INDICATOR). [HRMZ]        CODE INDICATING THE TYPE OF CLAIM RECORD BEING PROCESSED WITH RESPECT TO PAYMENT (DEBIT/CREDIT INDICATOR; INTERIM/FINAL INDICATOR). [NCH]

name: CLM_RAC_ADJSTMT_IND_CD
comment: A CODE INDICATING A RECOVERY AUDIT CONTRACTOR (RAC) REQUESTED AN ADJUSTMENT TO A CLAIM AS A RESULT OF POST-PAYMENT ACTIVITIES DONE BY THE RAC.  VALID VALUES:  R = RAC ADJUSTED CLAIM  SPACES = DOES NOT APPLY

name: CLM_RLT_COND_SGNTR_SK
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ASSIGNED SURROGATE KEY THAT UNIQUELY IDENTIFIES A COMBINATION OF RELATED CONDITIONS THAT HAVE CO-OCCURRED WITHIN SOME SET OF CLAIMS.

name: CLM_RLT_OCRNC_SGNTR_SK
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ASSIGNED SURROGATE KEY THAT UNIQUELY IDENTIFIES A COMBINATION OF RELATED OCCURRENCES THAT HAVE CO-OCCURRED WITHIN SOME SET OF CLAIMS.

name: CLM_SBMT_CHRG_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT TOTALING THE SUM OF ALL THE LINE ITEM SUBMITTED CHARGES ON A CLAIM.

name: CLM_SBMT_FRMT_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE SUBMITTED FORMAT OF A MEDICARE PART D PRESCRIPTION DRUG EVENT (PDE) CLAIM.  FOR EXAMPLE:  X = X12 837  B = BENEFICIARY SUBMITTED  P = PAPER CLAIM FROM PROVIDER    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_SBMT_FRMT_CD

name: CLM_SPND_DWN_AMT
comment: THE AMOUNT FOR WHICH THE MEDICAID RECIPIENT IS RESPONSIBLE AS PART OF THEIR SPEND DOWN AMOUNT.

name: CLM_UNIQ_ID
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ASSIGNED SURROGATE KEY USED TO IDENTIFY A CLAIM.

name: CLM_SRC_ID
comment: AN IDENTIFIER INDICATING WHERE THE SOURCE OF THE CLAIM DATA IN THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ORIGINATED FROM.   VALID VALUES:  20000 = NATIONAL CLAIMS HISTORY (NCH)  21000 = FISCAL INTERMEDIARY SHARED SYSTEM (FISS)  22000 = MULTI-CARRIER SYSTEM (MCS)  23000 = VIABLE INFORMATION PROCESSING SYSTEMS (VIPS) MEDICARE SYSTEM (VMS)  24000 = ENCOUNTER DATA PROCESSING SYSTEM (EDPS)  25000 = ENCOUNTER MEDICAID DUALS 837 CLAIMS  AND DUALS MEDICAID DRUG CLAIMS (DMDC)  N/A = MEDICAID

name: CLM_SRVC_UNIT_QTY
comment: A QUANTITY IDENTIFYING THE NUMBER OF SERVICES SUBMITTED ON A CLAIM.

name: CLM_DCMTN_CD
comment: A CODE INDICATING THE NUMBER OF ADDITIONAL DOCUMENTS A PROVIDER HAS SUBMITTED WITH AN ELECTRONIC CLAIM.  FOR EXAMPLE:  P1 = ONE ITERATION (ONE ADDITIONAL DOCUMENT SUBMITTED)  P7 = SEVEN ITERATIONS (SEVEN ADDITIONAL DOCUMENTS SUBMITTED)

name: BENE_SEX_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE GENDER OF A MEDICARE BENEFICIARY.     REFERENCE TABLE: BENE_SEX_CD

name: CLM_CNTRCTR_NUM
comment: A NUMBER ASSIGNED BY CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID SERVICES (CMS) IDENTIFYING A MEDICARE ADMINISTRATIVE CONTRACTOR (MAC) AUTHORIZED TO PROCESS MEDICARE CLAIMS.    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_CNTRCTR_NUM

name: GEO_FIPS_STATE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING A TWO-CHARACTER ALPHABETIC ABBREVIATION FOR A STATE DEFINED BY THE FEDERAL INFORMATION PROCESSING STANDARD (FIPS).    REFERENCE TABLE: GEO_FIPS_STATE_CD

name: CLM_ATNDG_PRVDR_NAME
comment: A FULL NAME FOR AN ATTENDING PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_ATNDG_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF AN ATTENDING PROVIDER.

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF THE BILLING PROVIDER ON THE CLAIM, AS PROVIDED BY THE SOURCE SYSTEM.

name: GEO_BLG_SSA_STATE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING A STATE AS DEFINED BY THE SOCIAL SECURITY ADMINISTRATION (SSA) STANDARD.

name: CLM_FAC_PRVDR_CPO_ORG_NPI_ID
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING A NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) UNIQUELY ASSIGNED TO A HEALTH CARE PROVIDER.   THIS NPI IS A HOME HEALTH AGENCY (HHA) OR HOSPICE THAT IS RENDERING MEDICARE SERVICES DURING THE PERIOD A PHYSICIAN IS PROVIDING CARE PLAN OVERSIGHT (CPO) SERVICES.

name: CLM_FAC_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING A NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) UNIQUELY ASSIGNED TO A HEALTH CARE PROVIDER.

name: GEO_FAC_SSA_STATE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING A STATE AS DEFINED BY THE SOCIAL SECURITY ADMINISTRATION (SSA) STANDARD. REFERENCE TABLE: GEO_SSA_STATE_CD

name: CLM_OPRTG_PRVDR_UPIN_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE UNIQUE PHYSICIAN IDENTIFICATION NUMBER (UPIN) OF AN OPERATING PROVIDER SUBMITTED ON CLAIM.

name: CLM_OPRTG_PRVDR_NAME
comment: A COMPLETE NAME IDENTIFYING THE OPERATING PROVIDER ON A CLAIM, A CONCATENATION OF  THE FIRST, MIDDLE, AND LAST NAME.

name: CLM_OPRTG_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF AN OPERATING PROVIDER SUBMITTED ON A CLAIM.

name: CLM_OTHR_PRVDR_UPIN_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE UNIQUE PHYSICIAN IDENTIFICATION NUMBER (UPIN) OF AN OTHER PROVIDER SUBMITTED ON CLAIM.

name: CLM_OTHR_PRVDR_NAME
comment: A COMPLETE NAME IDENTIFYING THE OTHER PROVIDER ON A CLAIM, FORMATTED AS FIRST, MIDDLE, AND LAST NAME FOR AN INDIVIDUAL PROVIDER.

name: CLM_OTHR_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF AN OTHER PROVIDER SUBMITTED ON A CLAIM.

name: CLM_PRSBNG_PRVDR_GNRC_ID_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING A GENERIC IDENTIFIER OF A PRESCRIBING PROVIDER SUBMITTED ON A DRUG CLAIM.

name: PRVDR_PRSBNG_ID_QLFYR_CD
comment: A CODE INDICATING THE TYPE OF NUMBER USED TO IDENTIFY A PRESCRIBING PROVIDER ON A CLAIM.  FOR EXAMPLE:  01 = NPI  07 = NCPDP NUMBER  08 = STATE LICENSE NUMBER    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_PRVDR_ID_QLFYR_CD

name: CLM_RFRG_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF A REFERRING PROVIDER SUBMITTED ON A CLAIM.

name: CLM_RFRG_PRVDR_PIN_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING A REFERRING PROVIDER AS ASSIGNED BY A MEDICARE ADMINISTRATIVE CONTRACTOR (MAC).

name: CLM_SRVC_PRVDR_GNRC_ID_NUM
comment: A NUMBER USED TO IDENTIFY A SERVICE PROVIDER.

name: PRVDR_SRVC_ID_QLFYR_CD
comment: A CODE INDICATING THE TYPE OF NUMBER USED TO IDENTIFY A SERVICE PROVIDER ON A CLAIM.  FOR EXAMPLE:  01 = NPI  07 = NCPDP NUMBER  08 = STATE LICENSE NUMBER    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_PRVDR_ID_QLFYR_CD

name: CLM_RIC_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE CLAIM RECORD TYPE BEING PROCESSED. VALID VALUES: W = PART B V = PART A U= BOTH

name: CLM_MDCR_PHASE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING WHICH PHASE OF THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) LIFECYCLE A SHARED SYSTEM CLAIM IS IN WHEN IT IS SENT TO THE IDR BY A SHARED SYSTEM MAINTAINER (SSM).     REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_MDCR_PHASE_CD

name: CLM_BILL_FREQ_CD
comment: A CODE INDICATING THE SEQUENCE OF AN INSTITUTIONAL CLAIM IN THE BENEFICIARYS CURRENT EPISODE OF CARE. IT IS THE THIRD DIGIT OF THE TYPE OF BILL (TOB).    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_BILL_FREQ_CD

name: CLM_MDCR_INCMPLT_PHASE_IND
comment: AN INDICATOR IDENTIFYING WHETHER A SHARED SYSTEM CLAIM HAS A PARENT OR PREDECESSOR CLAIM.  VALID VALUES:  Y = CLAIM DOES NOT HAVE A PREDECESSOR.  N =  CLAIM DOES HAVE A PREDECESSOR.

name: CLM_THRU_DT
comment: A DATE IDENTIFYING THE LAST DAY SERVICES ARE PROVIDED TO A BENEFICIARY.  NOTE: FOR DRUG CLAIMS, THIS DATE IS WHEN THE PRESCRIPTION WAS FILLED.

name: CLM_MASS_ADJSTMT_IND
comment: AN INDICATOR IDENTIFYING WHETHER THE CLAIM WAS ADJUDICATED AS PART OF A MASS ADJUSTMENT. VALID VALUES: Y = CLAIM WAS INCLUDED IN A MASS ADJUSTMENT N = CLAIM WAS NOT INCLUDED IN A MASS ADJUSTMENT

name: CLM_BLOOD_CHRG_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING THE TOTAL CHARGE FOR BLOOD USAGE.

name: CLM_BLOOD_NCVRD_CHRG_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING THE TOTAL NON-COVERED CHARGE FOR BLOOD USAGE.

name: CLM_BLOOD_LBLTY_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING THE PORTION OF THE BLOOD DEDUCTIBLE A BENEFICIARY IS LIABLE FOR.

name: CLM_BLOOD_PT_FRNSH_QTY
comment: A QUANTITY INDICATING THE  WHOLE PINTS OF BLOODS FURNISHED TO A BENEFICIARY.

name: CLM_BLOOD_PT_NRPLC_QTY
comment: A QUANTITY INDICATING THE WHOLE PINTS OF BLOOD NOT REPLACED FOR A BENEFICIARY.

name: CLM_BLOOD_PT_RPLC_QTY
comment: A QUANTITY INDICATING THE WHOLE PINTS OF BLOOD REPLACED FOR A BENEFICIARY.

name: CLM_PTA_BLOOD_DDCTBL_QTY
comment: A QUANTITY IDENTIFYING THE AMOUNT OF BLOOD PINTS APPLIED TO THE BLOOD DEDUCTIBLE FOR PART A CLAIMS.

name: CLM_BENE_INTRST_PD_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING THE INTEREST PAID TO A BENEFICIARY DUE TO A DELAY IN THE PAYMENT OF A CLAIM.

name: CLM_BENE_PD_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT PAID TO A BENEFICIARY FOR A SUBMITTED CLAIM.

name: CLM_BLG_CWF_SNCTN_PRVDR_IND
comment: AN INDICATOR IDENTIFYING IF A PROVIDER HAS BEEN SANCTIONED.  VALID VALUES:  S = PROVIDER IS SANCTIONED  BLANK = PROVIDER IS NOT SANCTIONED

name: CLM_BLG_FED_PRVDR_SPCLTY_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID SERVICES (CMS) SPECIALTY OF A PROVIDER OR SUPPLIER.  FOR EXAMPLE:  11 = INTERNAL MEDICINE  49 = AMBULATORY SURGICAL CENTER  REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_PRVDR_SPCLTY_CD

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_CNTY_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING A COUNTY AS ASSIGNED BY THE SOCIAL SECURITY ADMINISTRATION (SSA) STANDARD. REFERENCE TABLE: GEO_SSA_CNTY_CD

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_EIN_NUM
comment: AN EMPLOYER IDENTIFICATION NUMBER (EIN) ASSIGNED TO A BILLING PROVIDER.

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_LCLTY_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING A PROVIDERS GEOGRAPHIC LOCATION AS DEFINED BY CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID SERVICES (CMS) FOR USE IN PRICING/REIMBURSING A CLAIM.    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_CNTRCTR_LCLTY

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_PIN_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING A PROVIDER AS ASSIGNED BY A MEDICARE ADMINISTRATIVE CONTRACTOR (MAC).

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_PRTCPTG_CD
comment: A CODE INDICATING IF A PROVIDER IS PARTICIPATING OR ACCEPTING ASSIGNMENT FOR A CLAIM.

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_TAX_NUM
comment: A NUMBER ASSIGNED TO A PROVIDER BY THE FEDERAL GOVERNMENT FOR TAX REPORTING PURPOSES.

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_TYPE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE TYPE OF PROVIDER FURNISHING THE SERVICE ON A CLAIM. REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_PRVDR_TYPE_CD

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_USPS_STATE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE TWO-CHARACTER ALPHABETIC ABBREVIATION FOR A STATE IN THE UNITED STATES AS DEFINED BY THE UNITED STATES POSTAL SERVICE (USPS).    REFERENCE TABLE: GEO_USPS_STATE_CD

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_ZIP5_CD
comment: A FIVE-DIGIT ZIP CODE DEFINED BY THE UNITED STATES POSTAL SERVICE (USPS) THAT IDENTIFIES A DESTINATION POST OFFICE OR DELIVERY AREA ASSOCIATED WITH A BENEFICIARY, PROVIDER, OR CLAIM ADDRESS.    REFERENCE TABLE: GEO_ZIP5_CD

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_ZIP4_CD
comment: A FOUR-DIGIT ZIP CODE EXTENSION DEFINED BY THE UNITED STATES POSTAL SERVICE (USPS) THAT REPRESENTS A SPECIFIC DELIVERY ROUTE WITHIN A DELIVERY AREA ASSOCIATED WITH A BENEFICIARY, PROVIDER, OR CLAIM ADDRESS AND USED IN THE GEOCODING PROCESS. REFERENCE TABLE: GEO_ZIP9_CD

name: CLM_CLN_IND
comment: AN INDICATOR IDENTIFYING IF A CLAIM IS CLASSIFIED AS CLEAN OR DIRTY. THIS VALUE IS USED IN WORKLOAD AND CLAIMS PROCESSING TIMELINESS (CPT) REPORTING AND DETERMINES IF INTEREST SHOULD BE PAID ON A CLAIM WHEN IT IS NOT PAID WITHIN THE MANDATED PAYMENT TIMEFRAME.  FOR EXAMPLE:  C = CLEAN  D = DIRTY  O = OTHER THAN CLEAN  B =  PERIODIC INTERIM PAYMENTS (PIP) CLEAN  E = ADDITIONAL INFORMATION REQUESTED (NON-PIP)

name: CLM_FROM_DT
comment: A DATE IDENTIFYING THE FIRST DAY SERVICES ARE PROVIDED TO A BENEFICIARY.

name: CLM_PD_DT
comment: A DATE INDICATING WHEN A CLAIM WAS PAID.

name: CLM_RFRG_PRVDR_NAME
comment: A COMPLETE NAME IDENTIFYING THE REFERRING PROVIDER ON A CLAIM, A CONCATENATION OF  THE FIRST, MIDDLE, AND LAST NAME.

name: CLM_RFRG_PRVDR_UPIN_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE UNIQUE PHYSICIAN IDENTIFICATION NUMBER (UPIN) OF A REFERRING PROVIDER SUBMITTED ON CLAIM.

name: CLM_SBMTR_ID
comment: A VALUE IDENTIFYING THE SUBMITTER OF AN ELECTRONIC MEDIA CLAIM (EMC) CLAIM.    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_SBMTR

name: CLM_TOT_LINE_CNT
comment: A COUNT IDENTIFYING THE NUMBER OF DETAIL SERVICE LINES SUBMITTED ON A CLAIM.

name: CLM_XREF_HIC_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING A PRIOR HEALTH INSURANCE CLAIM NUMBER (HICN) USED TO CROSS REFERENCE TO A CORRECTED/NEW HICN FOR A BENEFICIARY.

name: CLM_OTHR_PRVDR_GNRC_ID_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING A GENERIC IDENTIFIER OF AN OTHER PROVIDER SUBMITTED ON A CLAIM.

name: PRVDR_OTHR_ID_QLFYR_CD
comment: A CODE INDICATING THE TYPE OF NUMBER USED TO IDENTIFY AN OTHER PROVIDER ON A CLAIM.  FOR EXAMPLE:  01 = NPI  07 = NCPDP NUMBER  08 = STATE LICENSE NUMBER    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_PRVDR_ID_QLFYR_CD

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_NSC_NUM
comment: A NUMBER ASSIGNED BY THE NATIONAL SUPPLIER CLEARINGHOUSE (NSC) TO A BILLING PROVIDER.

name: CLM_CHK_DT
comment: A DATE INDICATING WHEN A CHECK WAS GENERATED BY A MEDICARE ADMINISTRATIVE CONTRACTOR (MAC).

name: CLM_RA_DT
comment: A DATE IDENTIFYING WHEN THE REMITTANCE ADVICE (RA) WAS GENERATED FOR PAYMENT OR OTHER CLAIM ACTIONS.

name: CLM_ATNDG_PRVDR_UPIN_NUM
comment: A UNIQUE PHYSICIAN IDENTIFICATION NUMBER (UPIN) FOR AN ATTENDING PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_ATNDG_FED_PRVDR_SPCLTY_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID SERVICES (CMS) SPECIALTY OF A PROVIDER OR SUPPLIER.  FOR EXAMPLE:11 = INTERNAL MEDICINE  49 = AMBULATORY SURGICAL CENTER  REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_PRVDR_SPCLTY_CD

name: CLM_ATNDG_PRVDR_LAST_NAME
comment: A LAST NAME FOR AN ATTENDING PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_ATNDG_PRVDR_1ST_NAME
comment: A FIRST NAME FOR AN ATTENDING PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_ATNDG_PRVDR_MDL_NAME
comment: A MIDDLE NAME FOR AN ATTENDING PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_OSCAR_STATE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE TWO-DIGIT NUMERIC STATE FOR AN ONLINE SURVEY CERTIFICATION AND REPORTING (OSCAR) PROVIDER. THE OSCAR NUMBER IS GENERATED AND MAINTAINED BY THE CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID SERVICES (CMS) AND HAS BEEN RENAMED THE CMS CERTIFICATION NUMBER (CCN).

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_OSCAR_EMER_IND
comment: AN INDICATOR IDENTIFYING IF THE ONLINE SURVEY CERTIFICATION AND REPORT SYSTEM (OSCAR) NUMBER ASSIGNED TO A BILLING PROVIDER IS AN EMERGENCY HOSPITAL. THIS IS THE SIXTH POSITION OF THE PROVIDER NUMBER.   NOTE: THE OSCAR WAS RENAMED TO CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID (CMS) CERTIFICATION NUMBER (CCN) IN 2007 BY CMS.

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_OSCAR_NUM
comment: A NUMBER ASSIGNED TO A BILLING PROVIDER BY THE CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID SERVICES (CMS) VERIFYING THAT THE PROVIDER IS MEDICARE CERTIFIED AND FOR WHAT TYPES OF SERVICES .    NOTE: THE OSCAR WAS RENAMED TO CMS CERTIFICATION NUMBER (CCN) IN 2007 BY CMS.

name: CLM_OPRTG_FED_PRVDR_SPCLTY_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID SERVICES (CMS) SPECIALTY OF A PROVIDER OR SUPPLIER.  FOR EXAMPLE:  11 = INTERNAL MEDICINE  49 = AMBULATORY SURGICAL CENTER  REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_PRVDR_SPCLTY_CD

name: CLM_OPRTG_PRVDR_LAST_NAME
comment: A LAST NAME FOR AN OPERATING PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_OPRTG_PRVDR_1ST_NAME
comment: A FIRST NAME FOR AN OPERATING PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_OPRTG_PRVDR_MDL_NAME
comment: A MIDDLE NAME FOR AN OPERATING PROVIDER.

name: CLM_OTHR_FED_PRVDR_SPCLTY_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID SERVICES (CMS) SPECIALTY OF A PROVIDER OR SUPPLIER.  FOR EXAMPLE:  11 = INTERNAL MEDICINE  49 = AMBULATORY SURGICAL CENTER  REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_PRVDR_SPCLTY_CD

name: CLM_OTHR_PRVDR_LAST_NAME
comment: A LAST NAME FOR THE OTHER PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_OTHR_PRVDR_1ST_NAME
comment: A FIRST NAME FOR THE OTHER PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_OTHR_PRVDR_MDL_NAME
comment: A MIDDLE NAME FOR AN OTHER PROVIDER.

name: CLM_LCL_NCH_PRMRY_PYR_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE COVERAGE TYPE OF THE PRIMARY PAYER WHEN MEDICARE IS THE SECONDARY PAYER AS DEFINED BY THE SOURCE OF THE CLAIM DATA.  THE VALUE CAN DIFFER FOR THE SAME COVERAGE TYPE DEPENDING ON THE CLAIM SOURCE.  FOR EXAMPLE:      15 = WORKERS COMPENSATION (MULTI-CARRIER SYSTEM (MCS))      E = WORKERS COMPENSATION (FISCAL INTERMEDIARY SHARED SYSTEM (FISS))      W = WORKERS COMPENSATION (VIABLE INFORMATION PROCESSING SYSTEMS (VMS))    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_LCL_NCH_PRMRY_PYR_CD

name: CLM_LCL_SBMT_FRMT_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE SUBMITTED FORMAT OF A CLAIM AS DEFINED BY THE SOURCE OF THE CLAIM DATA.  FOR EXAMPLE:  8 = UB92 HARD COPY  D = NCPDP VERSION D.0 COMPOUND DRUG CLAIM  F = X12 837 5010 ELECTRONIC CLAIM    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_LCL_SBMT_FRMT_CD

name: CLM_NCH_PRMRY_PYR_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE COVERAGE TYPE OF THE PRIMARY PAYER WHEN MEDICARE IS THE SECONDARY PAYER AS DEFINED BY THE COMMON WORKING FILE (CWF).REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_NCH_PRMRY_PYR_CD

name: CLM_IDR_LD_DT
comment: A DATE IDENTIFYING WHEN PART A AND PART B DATA ARE LOADED INTO THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR).

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_OSCAR_FAC_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE ONLINE SURVEY CERTIFICATION AND REPORT SYSTEM (OSCAR) TYPE OF FACILITY FOR A BILLING PROVIDER. THIS IS POSITIONS 3-5 OF THE PROVIDER NUMBER.  NOTE: THE OSCAR WAS RENAMED TO CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID (CMS) CERTIFICATION NUMBER (CCN) IN 2007 BY CMS.

name: CLM_BILL_FAC_TYPE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE TYPE OF FACILITY THAT PROVIDED CARE TO A BENEFICIARY ON AN INSTITUTIONAL CLAIM. IT IS THE FIRST DIGIT OF THE TYPE OF BILL (TOB).    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_BILL_FAC_TYPE_CD

name: CLM_BILL_CLSFCTN_CD
comment: A CODE CLASSIFYING THE TYPE OF SERVICE PROVIDED TO A BENEFICIARY ON AN INSTITUTIONAL CLAIM. IT IS THE SECOND DIGIT OF THE TYPE OF BILL (TOB).    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_BILL_CLSFCTN_CD

name: CLM_RFRG_FED_PRVDR_SPCLTY_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID SERVICES (CMS) SPECIALTY OF A PROVIDER OR SUPPLIER.  FOR EXAMPLE:  11 = INTERNAL MEDICINE  49 = AMBULATORY SURGICAL CENTER  REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_PRVDR_SPCLTY_CD

name: CLM_RFRG_PRVDR_1ST_NAME
comment: A FIRST NAME FOR A REFERRING PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_RFRG_PRVDR_LAST_NAME
comment: A LAST NAME FOR A REFERRING PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_RFRG_PRVDR_MDL_NAME
comment: A MIDDLE NAME FOR A REFERRING PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_RNDRG_FED_PRVDR_SPCLTY_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID SERVICES (CMS) SPECIALTY OF A PROVIDER OR SUPPLIER.  FOR EXAMPLE:  11 = INTERNAL MEDICINE  49 = AMBULATORY SURGICAL CENTER  REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_PRVDR_SPCLTY_CD

name: CLM_RNDRG_PRVDR_1ST_NAME
comment: A FIRST NAME FOR A RENDERING PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_RNDRG_PRVDR_LAST_NAME
comment: A LAST NAME FOR A RENDERING PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_RNDRG_PRVDR_MDL_NAME
comment: A MIDDLE NAME FOR A RENDERING PHYSICIAN.

name: CLM_RNDRG_PRVDR_NAME
comment: A COMPLETE NAME IDENTIFYING THE REFERRING PROVIDER ON A CLAIM, A CONCATENATION OF  THE FIRST, MIDDLE, AND LAST NAME.

name: CLM_RNDRG_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF THE PROVIDER WHO RENDERED THE SERVICE, AS PROVIDED BY THE SOURCE SYSTEM.    NOTE: THIS COLUMN IS POPULATED FOR CERTAIN TYPES OF CLAIMS WHERE THE SAME RENDERING PROVIDER NPI APPLIES TO ALL LINES OF A CLAIM.

name: CLM_RNDRG_PRVDR_UPIN_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE UNIQUE PHYSICIAN IDENTIFICATION NUMBER (UPIN) OF A RENDERING PROVIDER SUBMITTED ON CLAIM.

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_TXNMY_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE TYPE, CLASSIFICATION, AND/OR SPECIALIZATION OF A PROVIDER.  FOR EXAMPLE:  207R00000X = INTERNAL MEDICINE  3416A0800X = AMBULANCE AIR TRANSPORT    REFERENCE TABLE: PRVDR_NCPDP_TXNMY_CD

name: CLM_RNDRG_PRVDR_TXNMY_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE TYPE, CLASSIFICATION, AND/OR SPECIALIZATION OF A PROVIDER.  FOR EXAMPLE:  207R00000X = INTERNAL MEDICINE  3416A0800X = AMBULANCE AIR TRANSPORT    REFERENCE TABLE: PRVDR_NCPDP_TXNMY_CD

name: GEO_BENE_SSA_STATE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING A STATE OF THE BENEFICIARYS RESIDENCE AS ASSIGNED BY THE SOCIAL SECURITY ADMINISTRATION (SSA) STANDARD.    REFERENCE TABLE: GEO_SSA_STATE_CD

name: GEO_BENE_SSA_CNTY_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING A COUNTY OF THE BENEFICIARYS RESIDENCE AS ASSIGNED BY THE SOCIAL SECURITY ADMINISTRATION (SSA) STANDARD.    REFERENCE TABLE: GEO_SSA_CNTY_CD

name: CLM_PRVDR_INTRST_PD_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING THE INTEREST PAID TO A PROVIDER DUE TO THE LATE PROCESSING OF A CLAIM.

name: CLM_PRVDR_OTAF_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING A PROVIDER'S OBLIGATED TO ACCEPT IN FULL (OTAF) FROM MEDICARE AS PAYMENT. A BENEFICIARY CANNOT BE CHARGED FOR ANY AMOUNT EXCEEDING THE OTAF TOTAL.

name: CLM_PRVDR_RMNG_DUE_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING HOW MUCH PAYMENT IS STILL OWED TO A PROVIDER MINUS PRIOR PAYMENTS, OFFSETS, OR ADJUSTMENTS ON A CLAIM.

name: GEO_BLG_SK
comment: AN INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) ASSIGNED NUMERIC SURROGATE KEY IDENTIFYING A PARTICULAR GEOGRAPHICAL LOCATION BY ITS FIVE-DIGIT ZIP CODE.

name: CLM_RA_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE REMITTANCE ADVICE STATEMENT GENERATED TO NOTIFY PROVIDERS OF FINALIZED PAYMENTS AND ADJUSTMENTS OF SUBMITTED CLAIMS.

name: PRVDR_RFRG_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF A REFERRING PROVIDER AS SOURCED FROM THE NPI CROSSWALK REFERENCE INFORMATION PROVIDED BY THE NATIONAL PLAN AND PROVIDER ENUMERATION SYSTEM (NPPES).

name: PRVDR_CPO_FAC_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF A CARE PLAN OVERSIGHT (CPO) FACILITY PROVIDER AS SOURCED FROM THE NPI CROSSWALK REFERENCE INFORMATION PROVIDED BY THE NATIONAL PLAN AND PROVIDER ENUMERATION SYSTEM (NPPES).

name: PRVDR_BLG_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF THE BILLING PROVIDER ASSOCIATED WITH THE CLAIM, AS SOURCED FROM THE NATIONAL PLAN AND PROVIDER ENUMERATION SYSTEM (NPPES).     NOTE: THIS COLUMN IS POPULATED IF THE BILLING PROVIDER NPI ON THE CLAIM, AS PROVIDED BY THE SOURCE SYSTEM, CAN BE FOUND IN THE INTEGRATED DEPOSIT REPOSITORY (IDR) PROVIDER DATA AS SOURCED FROM NPPES.

name: PRVDR_ATNDG_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF AN ATTENDING PROVIDER AS SOURCED FROM THE NPI CROSSWALK REFERENCE INFORMATION PROVIDED BY THE NATIONAL PLAN AND PROVIDER ENUMERATION SYSTEM (NPPES).

name: PRVDR_OPRTG_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF AN OPERATING PROVIDER AS SOURCED FROM THE NPI CROSSWALK REFERENCE INFORMATION PROVIDED BY THE NATIONAL PLAN AND PROVIDER ENUMERATION SYSTEM (NPPES).

name: PRVDR_OTHR_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF AN OTHER PROVIDER AS SOURCED FROM THE NPI CROSSWALK REFERENCE INFORMATION PROVIDED BY THE NATIONAL PLAN AND PROVIDER ENUMERATION SYSTEM (NPPES).

name: PRVDR_RNDRNG_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF THE PROVIDER WHO RENDERED THE SERVICE, AS SOURCED FROM THE NATIONAL PLAN AND PROVIDER ENUMERATION SYSTEM (NPPES).    NOTE: THIS COLUMN IS POPULATED FOR CERTAIN TYPES OF CLAIMS WHERE THE SAME RENDERING PROVIDER NPI APPLIES TO ALL LINES OF THE CLAIM, AND IF THE RENDERING PROVIDER NPI ON THE CLAIM, AS PROVIDED BY THE SOURCE SYSTEM, CAN BE FOUND IN THE INTEGRATED DEPOSIT REPOSITORY (IDR) PROVIDER DATA AS SOURCED FROM NPPES.

name: PRVDR_PRSCRBNG_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF A PRESCRIBING PROVIDER AS SOURCED FROM THE NPI CROSSWALK REFERENCE INFORMATION PROVIDED BY THE NATIONAL PLAN AND PROVIDER ENUMERATION SYSTEM (NPPES).

name: PRVDR_SRVC_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF A SERVICE PROVIDER AS SOURCED FROM THE NPI CROSSWALK REFERENCE INFORMATION PROVIDED BY THE NATIONAL PLAN AND PROVIDER ENUMERATION SYSTEM (NPPES).

name: CLM_FPS_MODEL_NUM
comment: A VALUE INDICATING THE ANALYTICAL MODEL SUBMITTED BY THE FRAUD PREVENTION SYSTEM (FPS) USED TO IDENTIFY A CLAIM THAT MAY BE HIGH RISK FOR FRAUD BASED ON SPECIFIC INFORMATION.

name: CLM_FPS_MSN_1_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE MEDICARE SUMMARY NOTICE (MSN) GENERATED TO A BENEFICIARY EXPLAINING CLAIM DECISIONS AND INFORMATION PROVIDED BY THE FRAUD PREVENTION SYSTEM (FPS). FOR EXAMPLE: 15.21 15.4 99.96. THERE CAN BE UP TO TWO MSN CODES PROVIDED BY FPS FOR A CLAIM. THIS IS 1 OF 2 OCCURRENCES.

name: CLM_FPS_MSN_2_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE MEDICARE SUMMARY NOTICE (MSN) GENERATED TO A BENEFICIARY EXPLAINING CLAIM DECISIONS AND INFORMATION PROVIDED BY THE FRAUD PREVENTION SYSTEM (FPS). FOR EXAMPLE: 15.21 15.4 99.96. THERE CAN BE UP TO TWO MSN CODES PROVIDED BY FPS FOR A CLAIM. THIS IS 2 OF 2 OCCURRENCES.

name: CLM_CNTRCT_OF_REC_CNTRCT_NUM
comment: A UNIQUE NUMBER ASSIGNED BY CMS TO THE CONTRACT BETWEEN CMS AND AN ORGANIZATION THAT OFFERS PRESCRIPTION DRUG COVERAGE.    PART D CONTRACT NUMBER FROM BENEFICIARY ENROLLMENT AS DOCUMENTED IN CMS DATABASES WHEN A PDE (PRESCRIPTION DRUG EVENT) IS SAVED AND ACCEPTED BY CMS

name: CLM_CNTRCT_OF_REC_PBP_NUM
comment: A UNIQUE NUMBER ASSIGNED TO IDENTIFIY A SPECIFIC PRESCRIPTION DRUG PLAN WITHIN A CONTRACT.  PLAN BENEFIT PACKAGE UNDER THE ORIGINAL CONTRACT OF RECORD AS DOCUMENTED IN CMS DATABASES

name: CLM_SBMTR_CNTRCT_NUM
comment: A UNIQUE NUMBER ASSIGNED BY CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID SERVICES (CMS) TO THE CONTRACT BETWEEN CMS AND AN ORGANIZATION THAT OFFERS PRESCRIPTION DRUG AND/OR MEDICARE ADVANTAGE COVERAGE.  THE TERM CONTRACT IS USED INTERCHANGEABLY WITH THE TERM PLAN. CONTRACT NUMBER FOR THE CONTRACT SUBMITTING THE PRESCRIPTION DRUG EVENT (PDE) AND/OR MEDICARE ADVANTAGE ENCOUNTER DATA.

name: CLM_SBMTR_CNTRCT_PBP_NUM
comment: A UNIQUE NUMBER ASSIGNED TO IDENTIFIY A SPECIFIC PRESCRIPTION DRUG PLAN WITHIN A CONTRACT.  PLAN BENEFIT PACKAGE (PBP) SUBMITTING THE PRESCRIPTION DRUG EVENT (PDE)DATA UNDER THE SUBMITTING CONTRACT

name: CLM_ATNDG_PRVDR_TXNMY_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE TYPE, CLASSIFICATION, AND/OR SPECIALIZATION OF A PROVIDER.  FOR EXAMPLE:  207R00000X = INTERNAL MEDICINE  3416A0800X = AMBULANCE AIR TRANSPORT    REFERENCE TABLE: PRVDR_NCPDP_TXNMY_CD

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_1ST_NAME
comment: A FIRST NAME FOR A BILLING PROVIDER.

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_LAST_NAME
comment: A LAST NAME FOR A BILLING PROVIDER.

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_MDL_NAME
comment: A MIDDLE NAME FOR A BILLING PROVIDER.

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_NAME
comment: A COMPLETE NAME IDENTIFYING THE BILLING PROVIDER ON A CLAIM, A CONCATENATION OF  THE FIRST, MIDDLE, AND LAST NAME.

comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE TYPE, CLASSIFICATION, AND/OR SPECIALIZATION OF A PROVIDER.  FOR EXAMPLE:  207R00000X = INTERNAL MEDICINE  3416A0800X = AMBULANCE AIR TRANSPORT    REFERENCE TABLE: PRVDR_NCPDP_TXNMY_CD

name: CLM_OTHR_PRVDR_TXNMY_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE TYPE, CLASSIFICATION, AND/OR SPECIALIZATION OF A PROVIDER.  FOR EXAMPLE:  207R00000X = INTERNAL MEDICINE  3416A0800X = AMBULANCE AIR TRANSPORT    REFERENCE TABLE: PRVDR_NCPDP_TXNMY_CD

name: CLM_RFRG_PRVDR_TXNMY_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE TYPE, CLASSIFICATION, AND/OR SPECIALIZATION OF A PROVIDER.  FOR EXAMPLE:  207R00000X = INTERNAL MEDICINE  3416A0800X = AMBULANCE AIR TRANSPORT    REFERENCE TABLE: PRVDR_NCPDP_TXNMY_CD

name: CLM_SRVC_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMERIC VALUE INDICATING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF THE SERVICE LOCATION PROVIDER OR THE SITE OF SERVICE (SOS) PROVIDER ON THE CLAIM.

name: CLM_SBMTR_USPS_STATE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE TWO-CHARACTER ALPHABETIC ABBREVIATION FOR A STATE IN THE UNITED STATES AS DEFINED BY THE UNITED STATES POSTAL SERVICE (USPS).    REFERENCE TABLE: GEO_USPS_STATE_CD

name: CLM_PRNT_CNTL_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE ORIGINAL CONTROL NUMBER ON ADJUSTMENT CLAIMS.

name: CLM_ALTRNT_SRVC_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF AN ALTERNATE SERVICE PROVIDER SUBMITTED ON A DRUG CLAIM.

name: CLM_MDCR_DUAL_ELGBLTY_SW
comment: AN INDICATOR IDENTIFYING WHETHER A BENEFICIARY IS ELIGIBLE FOR BOTH MEDICARE AND ANOTHER PROGRAM.  VALID VALUES:  Y = ELIGIBLE FOR BOTH  N = NOT ELIGIBLE FOR BOTH

name: CLM_PRSCRBNG_PRVDR_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF A PRESCRIBING PROVIDER SUBMITTED ON A DRUG CLAIM.

name: CLM_PCP_1ST_NAME
comment: A FIRST NAME FOR A PRIMARY CARE PROVIDER ON A DRUG CLAIM.

name: CLM_PCP_GNRC_ID_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING A GENERIC IDENTIFIER OF A PRIMARY CARE PHYSICIAN (PCP) SUBMITTED ON A CLAIM.

name: CLM_PCP_ID_QLFYR_CD
comment: A CODE INDICATING THE TYPE OF NUMBER USED TO IDENTIFY A PRIMARY CARE PROVIDER ON A CLAIM.  FOR EXAMPLE:  01 = NPI  07 = NCPDP NUMBER  08 = STATE LICENSE NUMBER    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_PRVDR_ID_QLFYR_CD

name: CLM_PCP_LAST_NAME
comment: A LAST NAME FOR A PRIMARY CARE PROVIDER ON A DRUG CLAIM.

name: CLM_PCP_NPI_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE NATIONAL PROVIDER IDENTIFIER (NPI) OF A PRIMARY CARE PHYSICIAN (PCP) SUBMITTED ON A CLAIM.

name: CLM_CHK_NUM
comment: A NUMBER PRINTED ON A CHECK MAILED TO A PROVIDER.

name: CLM_MDCR_PHASE_SQNC_NUM
comment: A VALUE SIGNIFYING THE SEQUENCE OF THE PHASE 1 CLAIM.

name: CLM_PTNT_BIRTH_DT
comment: A DATE IDENTIFYING WHEN A BENEFICIARY IS BORN.

name: CLM_SBMTR_NUM
comment: A NUMBER IDENTIFYING THE SUBMITTER OF AN ELECTRONIC MEDIA CLAIM (EMC) CLAIM.    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_SBMTR

name: CLM_TOT_CNTRCTL_AMT
comment: AN AMOUNT IDENTIFYING THE PORTION OF A CHARGE THAT EXCEEDS THE MAXIMUM ALLOWABLE AMOUNT OR A CONTRACTED FEE ARRANGEMENT FOR A SERVICE.

name: CLM_FINL_ACTN_RULE_CD
comment: A CODE IDENTIFYING THE FINAL ACTION TAKEN ON A CLAIM.    REFERENCE TABLE: CLM_FINL_ACTN_RULE_CD

name: BENE_SK_LKP_CD
comment: A CODE RETURNED BY THE COMMON BENE ROUTINE INDICATING THE COMBINATION OF KEYS USED TO LOOK UP OR RESTATE A BENEFICIARY SURROGATEKEY (BENE_SK).    REFERENCE TABLE: BENE_SK_LKP_CD

name: CLM_BENE_MBI_ID
comment: AN IDENTIFIER THAT UNIQUELY IDENTIFIES A BENEFICIARY AND REPLACES THE HEALTH INSURANCE CLAIM NUMBER (HICN) ON MEDICARE CARDS. THE FORMAT OF THE MEDICARE BENEFICIARY IDENTIFIER (MBI) IS 11-POSITIONS IN LENGTH AND CONTAINS THE FOLLOWING VALUES:  POSITION 1   NUMERIC VALUES: 1 - 9  POSITION 2   ALPHABETIC VALUES: A - Z (MINUS S, L, O, I, B, Z)  POSITION 3   ALPHANUMERIC VALUES: 0 - 9 AND A - Z (MINUS S, L, O, I, B, Z)  POSITION 4   NUMERIC VALUES: 0 - 9  POSITION 5   ALPHABETIC VALUES: A - Z (MINUS S, L, O, I, B, Z)  POSITION 6   ALPHANUMERIC VALUES: 0 - 9 AND A - Z (MINUS S, L, O, I, B, Z)  POSITION 7   NUMERIC VALUES: 0 - 9  POSITION 8   ALPHABETIC VALUES: A - Z (MINUS S, L, O, I, B, Z)  POSITION 9   ALPHABETIC VALUES: A - Z (MINUS S, L, O, I, B, Z)  POSITION 10   NUMERIC VALUES: 0 - 9  POSITION 11   NUMERIC VALUES: 0 - 9

name: BENE_ID_TYPE_CD
comment: A CODE INDICATING THE TYPE OF BENEFICIARY IDENTIFIER SUBMITTED ON A CLAIM.    REFERENCE TABLE: BENE_ID_TYPE_CD

name: CLM_IDE_NUM
comment: AN INVESTIGATIONAL DEVICE EXEMPTION (IDE) NUMBER ASSIGNED BY THE FOOD AND DRUG ADMINISTRATION (FDA) TO AN INVESTIGATIONAL DEVICE USED IN A CLINICAL TRIAL.

name: IDR_CLM_FMLY_ID
comment: AN IDENTIFIER ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) THAT UNIQUELY IDENTIFIES A FAMILY OF CLAIMS OR ENCOUNTERS WITHIN A GIVEN IDR DATA STREAM. A FAMILY CONSISTS OF CLAIMS OR ENCOUNTERS THAT ARE LINKED TO EACH OTHER (E.G. ORIGINAL AND REPLACEMENT).  THIS COLUMN IS POPULATED FOR MEDICARE ADVANTAGE (MA) ENCOUNTERS ONLY AT THIS TIME.

name: CLM_ADJSTMT_SQNC_NUM
comment: A NUMBER ASSIGNED BY THE EXTRACT, TRANSFORM, AND LOAD (ETL) PROCESS TO INDICATE THE SEQUENCE OF AN ADJUSTMENT IN A SINGLE CLAIM FAMILY.

name: CLM_VOID_SW
comment: AN INDICATOR IDENTIFYING WHETHER THE CLAIM IS A VOID (CLM_DISP_CD OF ‘03’, CLM_QUERY_CD OF ‘C’ OR CLM_BILL_FREQ_CD OF ‘8). VALID VALUES: Y = VOIDED CLAIM N = NOT A VOIDED CLAIM

name: CLM_CWF_APRVD_SW
comment: AN INDICATOR IDENTIFYING WHETHER THE CLAIM LINE HAS BEEN APPROVED BY THE COMMON WORKING FILE (CWF). VALID VALUES: Y = APPROVED BY CWF N= NOT APPROVED BY CWF

name: CLM_BLG_PRVDR_FULL_CCN_NUM
comment: A UNIQUE NUMBER ASSIGNED TO A BILLING PROVIDER BY THE CENTERS FOR MEDICARE AND MEDICAID SERVICES (CMS) TO IDENTIFY EACH SEPARATELY CERTIFIED MEDICARE PART A PROVIDER.  NOTE: THIS IS A FULL CMS CERTIFICATION NUMBER (CCN) THAT ALLOWS FOR THE IDENTIFICATION OF MULTIPLE CAMPUS HOSPITALS. FOR MULTI-CAMPUS HOSPITALS, ALL CAMPUSES CONTAIN THE SAME FIRST 6-DIGIT CCN, BUT POSITIONS 7-13 MAY BE USED TO DISTINGUISH BETWEEN CAMPUSES.

name: META_SK
comment: A UNIQUE LEGACY NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR), FORMULATED WITH A DATE AND A 3-DIGIT SEQUENCE NUMBER, WHICH IDENTIFIES THE BATCH PROCESS THAT INITIALLY LOADED A ROW IN THE IDR. DUE TO THE LIMITATION OF A 3-DIGIT VALUE, THIS IS BEING REPLACED BY META_SRC_PRCSG_ID ON NEW IDR TABLES AS THE SOURCE DATA TRACKING STANDARD.

name: META_LST_UPDT_SK
comment: A UNIQUE LEGACY NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR), FORMULATED WITH A DATE AND 3-DIGIT SEQUENCE NUMBER, WHICH IDENTIFIES THE BATCH PROCESS THAT UPDATED A ROW IN THE IDR. DUE TO THE LIMITATION OF A 3-DIGIT VALUE, THIS IS BEING REPLACED BY META_LTST_SRC_PRCSG_ID ON NEW IDR TABLES AS THE SOURCE DATA TRACKING STANDARD.

name: META_SRC_SK
comment: A UNIQUE NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) USED TO IDENTIFY THE SPECIFIC SOURCE OF THE DATA WHEN A ROW IS LOADED INTO THE IDR.    REFERENCE TABLE: V2_MDCR_META_DCTNRY_SRC

name: META_LST_UPDT_SRC_SK
comment: A UNIQUE NUMERIC VALUE ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) USED TO IDENTIFY THE SPECIFIC SOURCE OF THE DATA WHEN A ROW IS UPDATED IN THE IDR.

name: META_SRC_PRCSG_ID
comment: A VALUE ASSIGNED BASED ON A BATCH IDENTIFICATION IN ORDER TO TRACE IT BACK TO ITS ORIGINAL SOURCE. IT WILL ONLY BE POPULATED WHEN A RECORD IS INSERTED.

name: META_LTST_SRC_PRCSG_ID
comment: A VALUE ASSIGNED BASED ON A BATCH IDENTIFICATION IN ORDER TO TRACE IT BACK TO ITS ORIGINAL SOURCE. IT WILL ONLY BE POPULATED WHEN A RECORD IS SUBSEQUENTLY UPDATED.

name: IDR_INSRT_TS
comment: THE SYSTEM DATE AND TIME ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) WHILE PERFORMING AN INSERT OPERATION.

name: IDR_UPDT_TS
comment: THE SYSTEM DATE AND TIME ASSIGNED BY THE INTEGRATED DATA REPOSITORY (IDR) WHEN UPDATES ARE MADE TO ANY NON-PRIMARY KEY COLUMN.
